         <td>Peter Gallagher and Leonard Nimoy starred in NBC&#146;s world premiere movie &quot;Brave New World,&quot; based on Aldous Huxley&#146;s classic
            modern novel. The production was telecasted Sunday, May 3, 1998. Also starring are Miguel Ferrer, Academy Award nominee Sally Kirkland, Tim
         Guinee and Rya Kihlstedt.</td>
         <td><a href="http://us.imdb.com/title/tt0145600/" title="Brave New World, NBC version"><img border="1" height="78" width="150" src="w/pics/NBCbnw.jpg" alt="Brave New World NBC movie" /></a></td>
