      If you are seeking further information on Huxley or his works please see <a href="w/additional_resources.html">Additional Resources</a> or post your
      question in the <a href="https://www.tapatalk.com/groups/aldoushuxley/forum-f2/" title="message board">discussion forum</a>.</p>
   <p>Please do not plagiarize the compilation efforts of this site, however please feel free to link to any page. If you would like to contribute to this
      site <a href="http://somaweb.org/wp/contact/" title="Comments ONLY - Questions belong in the discussion forum!">send</a> any suggestions or links. To reference
      this site in your literary work see <a href="w/citation.html" title="Learn how to cite this web page">Citation Info</a>. This site has been viewed
      by millions of people and averages 46,000 unique visitors per annum. And for the curious, I am not Aldous' son Matthew. Happy reading!</p>
